title: Looking for a live/work space for a small / digital business?
posting_body: ['Incredible live/work space in the heart of Marina Del Rey!', 'A gorgeous 2-story townhouse above a commercial space.', 'It offers prime storefront visibility, street access, its own bathroom and private patio.', 'The upstairs townhome is a sun-drenched open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining.', 'The gourmet kitchen has a lovely balcony that is fantastic for grilling and outdoor dining.', 'The top-floor has a primary suite with a private balcony, walk-in closet and large bath.', 'Completing the 3rd floor is an additional sun-filled bedroom with en-suite bath.', 'Rounding out this gem are 3 side-by-side parking spaces, in-unit laundry, ample storage and building amenities such as a BBQ and fireplace, yoga/meditation room, guest parking and an amazing rooftop deck with city views.', 'To request a showing please reply with the date and time you would like to see the unit and the best number / email to contact you so we can confirm the appointment.', 'marina del rey, marina arts district, silicon beach, mar vista, culver city, live work loft, glencoe ave, abbot kinney blvd']
